  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large cast-iron skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add the diced onion and bell pepper to the skillet and cook until tender, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the crushed peanut cookies, thyme, rosemary, smoked paprika, garlic powder, salt, and black pepper to the skillet and stir to combine.",
    "Add the rest-meat to the skillet and cook, breaking it up with a spoon, until browned and crispy, about 5 minutes.",
    "Use a spatula to scrape up any browned bits from the bottom of the skillet and serve hot, garnished with fresh herbs if desired."
